{
  "texts": [
    "This article describes how one such model, ChatGPT, can be used in practice.",
    "For this paper, we use ChatGPT but what we lay out as practical steps can be applied to any LLM with an accessible user interface.",
    "We describe how we incorporated LLMs into our research practice through two working examples.",
    "The first example is the task of identifying different lifestyle items in politicians' Twitter self-descriptions.",
    "This task can be considered a form of index coding (Deterding & Waters 2021"
  ]
}